descripcion:
For setting tobacco transplants, sweet potato and other vegetable transplants, newly-set cuttings, and tree and shrub transplanting. Provides extra water soluble phosphorous to help stimulate root development. Excellent whenever tissue tests indicate the need for extra phosphate. No added micronutrients. If minor elements needed use Premium 9-45-15.

DERIVED FROM: Ammonium Phosphate, Potassium Phosphate, Potassium Sulfate F1367

POTENTIAL BASICITY: 1110 lbs calcium carbonate equivalent per ton.
